headline: Morgan Stanley Maintains Hold Rating on Adobe (ADBE) Stock
summary: Adobe Inc. (NASDAQ:ADBE) is one of the Best Monopoly Stocks to Buy Now. On October 30, Keith Weiss, an analyst from Morgan Stanley, maintained a “Hold” rating on the company’s stock.
